item.description: NH Jazz Center (nhjazz.com) at Pitman's Freight Room:TakeI93 north to exit 20,at end of ramp make left onto US3 towards Laconia.When US3 makes a right onto the Laconia/Gilford Bypass go straight on Court Street (US3B),Make a left onto Main Street (NH106),go over the old RR tracks and make a left onto New Salem Street.Shows every Thursday,doors open 7:15,$10 cover charge,BYOB, free popcorn.Show 8PM to 10:30pm.Manhattan style jazz club,good performers,lots of fun.---Steve---
item.name: Jazz-NH Jazz Center
